      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable, honest choice for a daily commuter. While it runs reliably, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches along the side panels and some fading on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery shows signs of regular use and minor staining, but all essential features and electronics are fully functional. It\u2019s a solid, practical car for someone who prioritizes mechanical performance over a perfect cosmetic appearance.",
