    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in such pristine, flawless condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' magic without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43900.0,
