    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing paintwork that retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark in sight. Step inside to an interior that still carries that distinct new-car aroma; the premium leather seats are supple, free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the dash remains pristine. Every switch, dial, and digital interface operates with the crisp precision of the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service dossier with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Underneath, the chassis is remarkably clean, showing no signs of inclement weather exposure. This sale includes the full set of original keys, all owner manuals in their leather folio, and a custom-fit breathable car cover. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 44900.0,
